    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically robust, having undergone essential subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure long-term valvetrain reliability. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise shift gates, delivering power to the rear wheels via the factory variable M-differential. The chassis remains composed with a refreshed suspension setup utilizing Bilstein dampers and poly-bushing upgrades. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its age, the performance envelope is fully intact, providing a visceral, analog driving experience.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
