      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility, presenting in an impressive state that reflects careful ownership. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, with only minor, negligible imperfections from standard road use. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the high-quality upholstery is clean and firm, and all electronic features\u2014from the premium sound system to the climate control\u2014operate exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having undergone regular fluid changes and a recent multi-point inspection. It drives straight and true, with a responsive transmission and a quiet, powerful engine. This is a dependable, well-documented vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the premium price tag. It comes with a complete set of service records and two sets of keys.",
      "price": 34500.0,
